lub from Waikato where he had moved, to bolster their team for the Roope Rooster competition. They defeated [[Richmond Bulldogs|Richmond]] and [[Marist Saints|Marist]] comprehensively before beating a slightly weakened [[City Rovers|City]] team (with [[Maurice Wetherall]] suffering from influenza, and [[Bill Davidson (rugby league)|Bill Davidson]] with a leg injury) in the final 14-8.\n\n===Round 1===\nAthletic had a forward ordered off early in their match with [[North Shore Albions|Devonport United]] but still managed to lead at halftime before conceding the lead and the match in the second half.\n{{rugbybox collapsible\n| date = 1 September\n| time = 3:00\n| home = Devonport\n| score = 21-16\n| report = <ref>{{cite news\n| title =Roope Rooster Contests/Devonport Beat Athletic\n| page =4\n| publisher =New Zealand Herald, Volume LX, Issue 18494\n| date = 1923-09-03\n| url = https://paperspast.natlib.govt.nz/newspapers/NZH19230903.2.8.1\n| accessdate = 2019-09-03}}</ref>\n| away = Athletic\n| try1 = A Harper, A Godick, Wheeler, [[Bert Laing]] 2\n| con1 = C Hand, [[Bert Laing]]\n| pen1 = C Hand\n| try2 = [[Bert Avery]], Miller\n| con2 = [[Craddock Dufty]] 2\n| pen2 = [[Craddock Dufty]] 3\n| stadium = Carlaw Park 1\n| attendance = 5000\n| referee = L Bull\n}}\n \n{{rugbybox collapsible\n| date = 1 September\n| time = 3:00\n| home = Marist\n| score =43-20\n| report = <ref>{{cite news\n| title =Roope Rooster Contests/Marist and Ponsonby Win\n| page =4\n| publisher =New Zealand Herald, Volume LX, Issue 18494\n| date = 1923-09-03\n| url = https://paperspast.natlib.govt.nz/newspapers/NZH19230903.2.8.1\n| accessdate = 2019-09-03}}</ref>\n| away = Newton\n| try1 = [[Bill Stormont]] 4, [[Hec Brisbane]] 3, [[John Lang (New Zealand rugby league)|John Lang]], B Foss\n| con1 = Stevens 6, [[Hec Brisbane]]\n| pen1 = [[Bill Stormont]]\n| try2 = [[Clarrie Polson]], Watson, Williams, [[Wally Somers]]\n| con2 = [[Clarrie Polson]], Unknown x 1\n| pen2 = [[Clarrie Polson]], Clark\n| stadium = Carlaw Park 2\n| attendance = 5000\n| referee = B Bouvaird\n}}\n \n{{rugbybox collapsible\n| date = 1 September\n| time = 3:00\n| home = Ponsonby\n| score = 43-18\n| report = <ref>{{cite news\n| title =Roope Rooster Contests/Marist and Ponsonby Win\n| page =4\n| publisher =New Zealand Herald, Volume LX, Issue 18494\n| date = 1923-09-03\n| url = https://paperspast.natlib.govt.nz/newspapers/NZH19230903.2.8.1\n| accessdate = 2019-09-03}}</ref>\n| away = Richmond\n| try1 = T Peckham 2, [[Frank Delgrosso]] 2, [[Thomas McClymont]], [[Ivan Littlewood]] 3, McMahon\n| con1 = [[Frank Delgrosso]], [[Thomas McClymont]] 3, [[Ivan Littlewood]] 3, W Hanlon\n| pen1 =\n| try2 = Butler 3, Barber\n| con2 = McNeil 2\n| pen2 = McNeil\n| stadium = Auckland Domain\n| attendance =\n| referee = W Murray\n}}\n \n===Semi Finals===\n{{rugbybox collapsible\n| date = 8 September\n| time = 3:00\n| home = City\n| score = 49-12\n| report = <ref>{{cite news\n| title =Roope Rooster Competition/City Outclasses Devonport\n| page =9\n| publisher =Auckland Star, Volume LIV, Issue 216\n| date = 1923-09-10\n| url =https://paperspast.natlib.govt.nz/newspapers/AS19230910.2.126\n| accessdate = 2019-09-03}}</ref>\n| away = Devonport\n| try1 = F Wilson 2, S Crewther, [[Ben Davidson (rugby league)|Ben Davidson]], Casey, [[George Davidson (athlete)|George Davidson]] 3, [[Maurice Wetherill]] 2, H Hawkes 2, McDonald\n| con1 = [[George Davidson (athlete)|George Davidson]] 3, S Crewther, H Hawkes\n| pen1 =\n| try2 = Harry Douglas, Smith\n| con2 = C Hand, [[Neville St George]]\n| pen2 = C Hand\n| stadium = Carlaw Park 1\n| attendance = 6000\n| referee = W Murray\n}}\n \n{{rugbybox collapsible\n| date = 8 September\n| time = 3:00\n| home = Ponsonby\n| score = 34-12\n| report = <ref>{{cite news\n| title =Roope Rooster Competition/Ponsonby Beats Marist\n| page =9\n| publisher =Auckland Star, Volume LIV, Issue 216\n| date = 1923-09-10\n| url =https://paperspast.natlib.govt.nz/newspapers/AS19230910.2.126\n| accessdat